---

<BaseLayout title="Research — Eric So" description="Published research by Eric So spanning behavioral finance, asset pricing, AI, and regulatory policy." accent="navy">
  <PageHeader label="Research" title="Publications" image="/images/backdrops/Sloan2.jpeg" />

  <section class="section sticky-intro" data-theme="light">
    <div class="sticky-intro-inner">
      <aside class="sticky-pane">
        <span class="section-label">Research Agenda</span>
        <h2 class="sticky-title">Applied AI — in markets, in advice, in classrooms.</h2>
        <p class="sticky-body">
          My research asks how AI changes the way investors, firms, and
          students reason about information and make decisions. Behavioral
          finance and information economics are the through-lines that
          anchor this work in how people — not just machines — actually
          behave.
        </p>
      </aside>
      <div class="reveal-pane">
        <article class="reveal-card">
          <span class="reveal-num">01</span>
          <h3 class="reveal-title">Applied AI in Financial Markets</h3>
          <p>How generative models, algorithmic traders, and machine-read text reshape price discovery, sentiment, and the flow of capital — including the fiscal and labor-market consequences as AI scales.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="reveal-card">
          <span class="reveal-num">02</span>
          <h3 class="reveal-title">AI Advisors &amp; Human Decisions</h3>
          <p>When people prefer an AI advisor over a human one, what makes AI advice trusted or ignored, and the comparative advantage of machines for sensitive disclosures.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="reveal-card">
          <span class="reveal-num">03</span>
          <h3 class="reveal-title">Behavioral Finance &amp; Information</h3>
          <p>How biases, expectations, and information asymmetries shape returns — from analyst forecast errors and press tilt to liquidity around earnings announcements.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="reveal-card">
          <span class="reveal-num">04</span>
          <h3 class="reveal-title">Emergent Behavior of AI Models</h3>
          <p>How large models exhibit capabilities, biases, and failure modes that weren't explicitly designed in — and what those emergent behaviors mean for deploying them in high-stakes financial decisions.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <FeaturedResearch />

  {categories.map((cat) => (
    <section class="section" data-theme="light">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <h2 class="category-title">{cat.name}</h2>
        <div class="papers-list">
          {cat.papers.map((paper) => (
            <article class="paper-item">
              {paper.link ? (
                <a href={paper.link} class="paper-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  <h3 class="paper-title">{paper.title}</h3>
                </a>
              ) : (
                <h3 class="paper-title">{paper.title}</h3>
              )}
              <p class="paper-authors">{paper.authors}</p>
              <p class="paper-journal">
                <em>{paper.journal}</em> — {paper.volume}
              </p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  ))}
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* --- Scrollytelling intro: sticky pane on the left, scrolling cards on the right --- */
  .sticky-intro {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .sticky-intro-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--section-pad-x);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(260px, 1fr) 1.4fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .sticky-pane {
    position: sticky;
    top: 7rem;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .sticky-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .sticky-body {
    color: var(--gray-600);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 42ch;
  }

  .reveal-pane {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 40vh; /* extra scroll runway so the last card still shows alongside the sticky pane */
  }

  .reveal-card {
    padding: 2rem 2rem 2rem 2.2rem;
    background: var(--pure-white);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    transition: opacity 0.55s ease, transform 0.55s ease;
  }

  .reveal-card.is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
  }

  .reveal-num {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .reveal-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .reveal-card p {
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .sticky-intro-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .sticky-pane {
      position: static;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .reveal-pane {
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .reveal-card {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none;
      transition: none;
    }
  }

  .category-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--black);
  }

  .papers-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .paper-item {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
  }

  .paper-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .paper-title {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .paper-link {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .paper-link:hover .paper-title {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .paper-link:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .paper-authors {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .paper-journal {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }
</style>

<script is:inline data-astro-rerun>
  // Stagger-reveal the scrollytelling cards as they scroll into view.
  (function () {
    const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal-card');
    if (!cards.length) return;
    const io = new IntersectionObserver(
      (entries) => {
        entries.forEach((entry) => {
          if (entry.isIntersecting) {
            entry.target.classList.add('is-visible');
            io.unobserve(entry.target);
          }
        });
      },
      { rootMargin: '0px 0px -20% 0px', threshold: 0.1 }
    );
    cards.forEach((c) => io.observe(c));
  })();
</script>
